<Layout title="Mimecom - Digital Therapy" classes="grid place-items-center h-full w-full">
  <section>
    <p>When you need a</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-300 mt-4">- Website Done</h1>
    <p class="text-green-200">
      Need a portfolio? A simple site? A complicated one? A business site? A
      shop? I can help you set it up, host it, maintain it. I design and
      program. Using Astro, Shopify, or whatever fits your needs best. Fast,
      secure, reliable. Including domain name advice and setup, email setup, SEO
      basics, analytics, backups, updates, security hardening and more.
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-300 mt-4">- Digital Handyman</h1>
    <p class="text-green-200">
      Planning your smarter home. Selecting the right things. Wifi - Mesh or not
      and where to place it. Printers (no, there is no perfect printer). Putting
      it all together. Apple problems and solutions. Linux (what?) anything.
      Backup plans. Cable management. How to do X. With Z. Best security
      practices. Explain things like you are five years old. Explain it like you
      are 52 years old who isn't very technical. Listen to your gripes with
      technology with great patience and sympathy. And solve your problems. Just
      like therapy but digital - digital therapy.
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-300 mt-4">- Your Car Repaired</h1>
    <p class="text-green-200">
      I am not your man. But I do know a great mechanic in Tangiers who is fair,
      honest, reliable and good at what he does. Here? I heard of one who is
      honest.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section style="hidden">
    <p>When you need to know my</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-300 mt-4">- Rates</h2>
